column3: Automatic sanity-testing: PASSED, see http://jenkins.bluematt.me/pull-tester/283f60eaf739dedc8321a755d1f94f02d69cb73e for binaries and test log.\nThis test script verifies pulls every time they are updated. It, however, dies sometimes and fails to test properly.  If you are waiting on a test, please check timestamps to verify that the test.log is moving at http://jenkins.bluematt.me/pull-tester/cu
FYI the last use of this was removed in commit c2efd981aa14e94cce4a0a888b6ee1f4e4347924, back when the IRC bootstrapping code was removed.\n
